textfsm_template:
Value ID (\d+)
Value SEVERITY (\S+)
Value TIME (\d+-\d+-\d+ \d+:\d+:\d+)
Value COMPONENT (\S+)
Value MESSAGE (.*)

Start
  ^\s*ID\s+Severity\s+Time\s+Component\s+Message\s*$$
  ^\s*${ID}\s+${SEVERITY}\s+${TIME}\s+${COMPONENT}\s+${MESSAGE}\s*$$ -> Record
